# Corpus (course material — too heavy for git; ~1.1 GB of PDF/DOCX/PPTX).
# Track only the README at corpus root; ignore everything else (raw export,
# weekly material, kotlin slide decks, binaries). Re-populate locally from
# the Drive folder referenced in corpus/README.md.
corpus/*
!corpus/README.md
!corpus/.gitignore

.ollama.log
